1) To uninstall particular Ruby version
     -- rvm uninstall 2.0.0


2) Reset to previous RVM state
     -- rvm reset

3) Use the user set default ruby
     -- rvm default

4) Switch to system gems directory
     -- rvm gemdir system

5) Equivalent to -->  rvm use 2.1.1
     -- rvm 2.1.1

6) To get help for commands on rvm
     -- rvm help

7) Reload rvm source itself
     -- rvm reload

8) Remove all default and system settings
    -- rvm reset 
